quran[286]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  2,2,"Ndeen deftere sikke alaa he mayre, ko nde peewal wonande hul…ďe …ďe"
  2,3,∆Āeen goon…óinoo…ďe mbirniindi e…ďe √Īii…ďna juulde e…ďe nafga e ko Min nje…ói …ďe
  2,4,"E …ďeen goon…óinoo…ďe ko Min njippini dow maa e ko jippinaa ado ma, e…ďe njananaa √Īalaande wattan"
  2,5,"∆Āeen dey ngoni ko e peewal iwngal e Joomii …ďe, ko kam…ďe ngoni da…óoo…ďe"
  2,6,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe ngoon…óintaa foti a jeertinii …ďe wolla a jeertinaani, fof foti e mum en"
  2,7,"Alla muppi …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, wirngallo woni noppi e gite ma…ď…ďe lette maw…óe na woodani …ďe"
  2,8,"Na woodi heen yim…ďe wi'oo…ďe min ngoon…óinii Alla e √Īalaande wattan, tawa …ďe ngoon…óinaani"
  2,9,"E…ďe koda Alla e goon…óin…ďe …ďe, alaa mbo …ďe kodata sonaa ko'e ma…ď…ďe tawa …ďe nganndaa"
  2,10,Ko √Īawo woni e …ďer…óe Alla …ďeydani …ďe √Īawu maa lette muus…óe njan e mum en sabu ko …ďe pennannoo
  2,11,So …ďe mbi'aama taa bonnee e lesdi ndi …ďe mbi'a minen ko min mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe
  2,12,Ko kam…ďe tigi ngoni bonnoo…ďe kono …ďe tinataa …óum
  2,13,"So …ďe mbi'aama ngoon…óinee wano yim…ďe …ďee ngoon…óiri, …ďe mbi'a mbela minen ngoon…óina wano …óaay…ďe …ďee ngoon…óiniri, kono ko kam…ďe tigi ngoni …óaay…ďe kono …ďe nganndaa"
  2,14,"So tawii …ďe kawrii e goon…óin…ďe …ďe mbi'a: min ngoon…óinii, so …ďe njeewdii e sey…óanooji ma…ď…ďe …ói …ďe mbi'a: minen ko onon min ngonndi min njalkitat tan"
  2,15,Alla jalkita …ďe O …ďeydana …ďe bewre …ďe ngona e wemmbere
  2,16,"Ko …ďeen ngoni soodir…ďe peewal majjere njeeygu ma…ď…ďe alaa tono, te …ďe peewaano"
  2,17,∆Āe nanndi ko e ku…ď…ďu…óo jayngol nde ngol yaynii Alla nawi ooyre ma…ď…ďe O acci …ďe e ni…ďe …ďe nji'ataa hay huunde
  2,18,Ko fah…óu…ďe muum…óu…ďe wum…ďe …ďe nduttotaako
  2,19,Wolla wano to…ďo iwde asamaan na woodi ni…ďe e digaali e maje …ďe cukka noppi ma…ď…ďe sabu kartaali (par√Īite) ngam reentaade maayde Alla noon Ombo hi…ďindii ge…óe heefer…ďe
  2,20,"Majal ngal na …óe…ďa yulde gite ma…ď…ďe kala nde ngal yaynii …ďe njaha heen so ni…ď…ďi…óii …ďe ndaroo, so Alla welano nawa nan…óe e gite ma…ď…ďe sabu Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde"
  2,21,Onon yim…ďe ndewee Jooma mon tag…óo on tagi adii…ďe on mbela joo kulon Alla
  2,22,"Oon mba…óan…óo on lesdi ndi mbertu O wa…ói Asamaan o mahoodi tii…óndi O jippini ndiyam iwde e Asamaan O yaltini heen …ďi…ď…ďe le…ó…óe woni nje…óu mon, taa mba…óanee Alla nanndidii…ďe te o…óon nganndi goonga o"
  2,23,"So tawii o…óon cikkitii e Kur'aana mbo Min njippini dow jeyaa…óo Amen o, ngaddee simoore nanndunde hembo, nodde wallidii…ďe mon gaa Alla so tawii o…óon ngoon…ói e nodditaandu mon ndu"
  2,24,"So tawii on mba…óaani …óum -te on mbaawataa …óum- kulee jayngol ku…ď…ďirtengol yim…ďe e kaa∆īe, ngol heblanaa ko heefer…ďe …ďe"
  2,25,"Weltin …ďeen goon…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īi wonde …ďe…ď ke…ďa aljannaaji caalli na ndonga les majji kala nde …ďe nje…óaa toon …ďi…ď…ďe le…ó…óe …ďe mbi'a ko …óee min nje…óanoo ko adii, kono si …ďe mee…óii …óe …ďe tawa e…óe ceerti, e…ďe ke…ďa toon rew…ďe laa…ď…ďe …ďe √Īii…ďida toon. @Corrected"
  2,26,"Alla aamantaa addude yeru hay so wonii wano …ďowngu e ko …ďuri …óum, so tawii ko goon…óin…ďe e…ďe nganndi ko goonga iw…óo e Jooma ma…ď…ďe, so tawii ko yeddu…ďe …ďe mbi'a holko Alla yi…ói e oo yeru Ombo majjina heew…ďe O feewna heen heew…ďe, alaa majjintee…óo heen sonaa yaltu…ďe …óoftaare. @Corrected"
  2,27,∆Āeen firtoo…ďe aadi Alla …ďaawo tii…óneede mbo e…ďe ta∆īa ko Alla yamiri yo jokke e…ďe mbonna ka lesdi ko kam…ďe ngoni rus…ďii…ďe (pertu…ďe)
  2,28,Holno njeddirton Alla tawa ngoodaano O wuurni on rewa heen O wara on rewa heen O wuurtina on …ďaawo …óuum ko e Makko nduttoto-…óon
  2,29,Kanko tagani on kala ko woni e lesdi ndi …ďaawo …óuum O faandii asamaan O fotndi mbo asamaanji jee…ói…ói Kanko ganndu…óo kala huunde. @Corrected
  2,30,"Nde Joom maa wi'i malayka en maa Mi wa…ó lomto Am e lesdi ndi, …ďe mbi'i mbela wa…óat heen bonnoowo dufoowo ∆īii∆īe tawa minen ko Aan tan min njettata mi…óen Ma teddina, O wi'i Miin Mi…óo anndi ko on nganndaa"
  2,31,"O anndini Aadama in…óe …óe fofo, rewi heen O holli …óe malaykaa…ďe …ďe O wi'i kaalanee Kam in…óe …ďee …óoo so tawii o…óon ngoon…ói"
  2,32,∆Āe mbi'i senaande woodanii Ma alaa ko min nganndi sonaa ko nganndin-∆äaa min ko Aan tan woni ganndid…óo kala huunde √Īee√Ī…óu…óo
  2,33,O wi'i aan Aadama anndin …ďe in…óe majji nde o anndini …ďe in…óe …óee O wi'i mbela Mi wi'aano on Miin Mi…óo anndi mbirniindi asamanji e lesdi Mi…óo anndi ko pe√Ī√Īinton e ko cuu…óoton fof
  2,34,Nde Min mbii malaykaa…ďe …ďe cujjanee Aadama …ďe cujji sonaa Ibliisa o salii o mawnikinii ndeen o jeyaa e yeddu…ďe
  2,35,Min mbii aan Aadama yah ho…óoy aljanna aan e debbo maa √Īaamee toon ko welata on kala …óo mbela-…óon taa …ďado-…óee kii lekki ndeen on jeyete e too√Ī…ďe
  2,36,Sey…óaane hoomti …ďe haa yaltini …ďe e mo∆ī∆īere nde …ďe ngonndoo Min mbii …ďe njippo-…óee ngonon a√Īondir…ďe ke…ďon √Īii…ďal dow lesdi ndi e dakmitaare haa happu yonta
  2,37,Aadama he…ďi konngi iwde e Joom mum O accani mo ko Kanko woni jaafotoo…óo jurmotoo…óo
  2,38,Min mbi'i njippo-…óee toon onon fof so tawii Mi addii e mon peewal kala dew…óo peewam Am …ďeen dey kulol alanaa …ďe kadi …ďe cunotaako
  2,39,∆Āeen yeddu…ďe penni maandeeji Amen ko …ďeen ngoni yim…ďe jayngol ko toon …ďe √Īii…ďata
  2,40,Onon …ďi…ď…ďe Isra'iil ciftoree mo∆ī∆īere Am nde Mi wa…óani on njottinee aadi Am Mi yottina aadi mon te kulon Kam Miin tan
  2,41,"Ngoon…óinee ko njippin-Mi na goon…óini ko njogi-…óon ko taa ngonee adii…ďe yeddude …óum wota on eto soodirde aayeeje am …óe coggu hoyngu, kulee kam Miin tan"
  2,42,Taa jii…ďindiree goonga e fenaande o…óon cuu…óa goonga o tawa o…óon nganndi mbo
  2,43,√Ďii…ďnee juulde tottiron asakal …óigganon njankinano-…óon Alla
  2,44,"Mbela on njamirat yim…ďe …óiggere njejjiton ko'e mon tawa o…óon njanga deftere nde, mbela on kakkilantaa …óum"
  2,45,"Mballitoree mu√Īal e juulde, pellet honde sa…ótani dow mbo yankinii…ďe …ďe"
  2,46,∆Āeen yananaa…ďe maa kawru e joom ma…ď…ďe ko he Makko …ďe nduttotoo
  2,47,"Onon …ďi…ď…ďe Isra'iil ciftoree neemaaji Am …ói neemin MI mon, ko Miin tigi …ďurni e dow winndre he"
  2,48,Kulee √Īande fittaandu alaa ko waawani fittandu wonndu ndu ja…ďantaake tefangol go…ó…óo coodtiigu kadi ja…ďetaake …ďe ke…ďataa ballo
  2,49,"Tuma Min ndanndii on yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďe mba…óii on lette bon…óe …ďe kirsa …ďi…ď…ďe mon …ďe ngoppa rew…ďe mon nguura, ina e …óuum lette maw…óe iwde ga Jooma mon"
  2,50,Nde Min peccani on maayo ngo Min ndanndi on Min njooli yim…ďe Fir'awna o…óon ndaarda gite mon Ňčaas
  2,51,Nde Min podani Muusaa jammaaji capan…óe nayi fawii heen ndew-…óon ngaari ndi caggal Am onon ko on too√Īoo…ďe
  2,52,Fawii heen Min ngaccani on …ďaawo …óuum mbela joo njetton
  2,53,Nde Min ngaddani Muusa deftere nde e Furgaana mbela joo peewon
  2,54,Nde Muusaa wi'i yim…ďe makko onon yim…ďe am on too√Īii ko'e mon nde ndew-…óon ngaari ndi ndutto…óee e tag…óo on o mbarto-…óon …óuum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īande on to Jooma mon O accana on Kanko woni gaccanoowo njurmotoo…óo
  2,55,Nde mbii-…óon Muusaa min ngoon…óitaa haa min nji'a Alla ko laa…ďi ndeen hartaango (jayngol iwde asamaan) …ďami on o…óon ndaarda gite mon
  2,56,Fawii heen Min nguurtini on …ďaawo nde maay-…óon mbela joo njetton
  2,57,"Min …óuwdini on duule Min njippinani on njuumri dakmundi e colli ju…óaa…ói √Īaamee e bel…ói ko Min nje…ói on, wonaa Minen …ďe too√Īi ko ko'e ma…ď…ďe …ďe too√Īatnoo"
  2,58,Min mbii naatee ndee saare √Īaamon heen ko mbela-…óon mbeltoron naatee damal ngal o…óon njankinii mbi'on accan min ndeen Min njaafoo on goopi mon Min …ďeydana mo∆ī∆īin…ďe …ďee mo∆ī∆īereeji
  2,59,Too√Ī…ďe …ďee mbayliti konngol ngol …ďe mbi'anoo ndeen Min njippini dow too√Īoo…ďe …ďee lette sabu ko …ďe ngonno ko faasqeebe
  2,60,"Nde Muusaa toranii yim…ďe mum ndiyam Min mbi'i fiyu haayre nde sawru maa ndu ndeen gite ndiyam sappo e …ói…ói puccitii heen yim…ďe …ďee fof ke…ďi yarde, √Īaamee njaree e nje…óu Alla taa mba…óee bonannde dow lesdi ndi"
  2,61,"Nde mbii-…óon aan Muusaa min min njondintaako e √Īaamdu wooturu torano min Joom maa O yaltinana min pu…ói lesdi gila e kappe e haakooji e buudi e √Īebbe e basalle (jabaa) mayri o, wi'i mbela on nji…ó lomtinde ko ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude ko, ke…ďon ko …ďuri jaasde …óuum njippo-…óee Misara maa on ke…ď ko tori-…óon ko …ďe pawaa koyeera e woro…óde …ďe nduttorii e tikkere Alla sabu …ďe njedduno aayeeje e…ďe mbara Annabaa…ďe ko aldaa e goonga …óuum noon ko goopi e too√Īe ma…ď…ďe"
  2,62,"∆Āeen goon…óin…ďe e…ď…ďen feew…ďe e nasaara en e …ďe ngalaa diine,kala goon…óin…óo Alla e √Īalaande wattan o golli ko mo∆ī∆īi …ďeen ke…ďata njo…ďdi to Jooma ma…ď…ďe kulol alanaa …ďe te kam…ďe …ďe cunotaako"
  2,63,Nde Min …ďami aadi mon Min ummini fello Tuur dow mon ∆īettee ko Min ngddani on e semmbe ciftoree ko woni heen mbela joo kulon Alla
  2,64,Fawii heen caggal …óuum nduŇčti-…óon taw naano …ďural Alla e yurmeende Makko dow mon maa on njeye e bonnoraa…ďe
  2,65,On nganndii …ďeen too√Ī…ďe e mon √Īande hoore-biir (samdi) Min mbii …ďe ngontee baa…ói booraa…ói
  2,66,Min mba…ói …óum woni maande teskuye wonande …ďe e aroyoo…ďe e tinndinoore wonande hul…ďe Alla …ďe
  2,67,"Muusaa wi'i yim…ďe makko Alla yamirii on nde kirsoton nagge …ďe mbii mbela nanngir-…óaa min ko …óaay…ďe? o wi'i: mi…óo moolii Alla jeyeede e majju…ďe"
  2,68,"∆Āe mbii du'ano min Jooma maa O la…ď…ďinana min no nge wa'i. O wii: ko nge wonaa nayeye wonaa √Īalel ko hakindiinge mba…óee ko njamira-…óon ko"
  2,69,"∆Āe mbii torano min Jooma maa O la…ď…ďinana min ngoobu (kulor) magge ? O wii: Oon wii ko sooye no feewi enge weli laarde"
  2,70,∆Āe mbii du'ano min Joom maa O la…ď…ďinana min no nge wa'i sabu na'i …ói nanndiri min maa min njiitu nge
  2,71,"O wi'i Kanko dee O wii ko nagge ne'iraange golle remru ngesa, kono wonaa yarnude gese, ko hisnge nge jillaani, …ďe mbii jooni dey a addii goonga …ďe kirsi nge kono …ďe …óe…ďaani wa…óde yamiroore nde"
  2,72,Nde mbar-…óon fettaandu ngon-…óon e tuumondirde ko Alla yaltini ko cuu…óno-…óon
  2,73,Min mbii tappindiree …ói ko noon Alla wuurtinirta maay…ďe O holla on kaawase Makko mbela joo kakkilon
  2,74,"Fawii heen …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óe njoori …ďaawo …óuum …óe mba'i no kaa∆īe maa …ďura noon, sabu kaa∆īe na ngoodi jaltinooje caalli go…ó…óe na peecoo njaltina ndiyam go…ó…óe kadi njowtoo janansabu hulde Alla, Alla noo yeebotaako ko ngolloton ko"
  2,75,Mbela o…óon …óaminii maa …ďe ngoon…óinan on tawa na woodi e ma…ď…ďe sete nanoowo haala Alla …ďe mbaylita ka caggal nde …ďe paami …ďe nganndi ka
  2,76,"So …ďe kawri e goon…óin…ďe …ďee …ďe mbii min ngoon…óinii so …ďe njeewdii …ďe mbi'a mbela on kaalanat …ďe ko Alla udditani on, ndeen …ďe ka…ďora on …óum to Jooma mon, mbela on kakkilantaa"
  2,77,Mbela …ďe nganndataa wonde Alla Mbo anndi ko …ďe cuu…óta e ko …ďe …ďaŇčnginta
  2,78,"Na woodi e mum en humambinnee…ďe …ďe nganndaa e deftere nde sonaa janngugol penaale …óe …ďe nganndinaa, …ďe ngoni e sikkude tan"
  2,79,"Bone woodanii …ďeen winndiroo…ďe deftere nde juu…óe ma…ď…ďe e…ďe mbi'a …óum ko to Alla iwri haa …ďe coodira nde coggu hoyngu, bone wonan …ďe e ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe mbinndi e kala ko …ďe paggitii heen"
  2,80,∆Āe mbii jayngol memataa min sinaa bal…óe see…óa wii …ďe mbela on ke…ďii fodoore Alla te Alla luutndotaako aadi Makko wolla ngon-…óon ko haalde e Alla ko on nganndanaa
  2,81,"Ko goonga kala mbo faggitii bonannde bon…ói makko piilii mo, ko …ďeen ngoni yim…ďe jayngol luttoo…ďe toon"
  2,82,∆Āeen goon…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īereeji ko …ďeen ngoni yim…ďe aljanna luttoo…ďe toon
  2,83,Min …ďamii fodoore e …ďi…ď…ďe Isra'iil taa ndewee sonaa Alla mo∆ī∆īon e jibnaa…ďe e jiidaa…ďe e waay…óu…ďe e waas…ďe o…óon kaalana yim…ďe …ďe ko mo∆ī∆īi darnon juulde tottiron asakal …ďaawo …óuum cali-…óon …óuurni-…óon sonaa see…óa e moo…óon
  2,84,Nde Min ∆īetti fodoore mon wota on nduf ∆īii∆īe mon taa on njaltin ko'e mon galleeji mon …ói ndeen nja…ď-…óon ceedi…óon …óum
  2,85,"Rewi heen onon …ďee o…óon mbara ko'e mon o…óon njaltina yim…ďe e mon galleeji ma…ď…ďe, o…óon pe√Ī√Īina too√Īe mon e ma…ď…ďe, si …ďe arii e mon dahaa…ďe coodtidon…ďe yaltingol …ďe na harmi e mon, mbela on goon…óinat yoga e deftere nde njeddon yoga heen kala e mon wa…óoo…ďe …óum njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ko koyeera weejo aduna √Īande darnga …ďe nduttee e lette …ďur…óe bonde Alla noon yeebotaako ko ngolloton ko"
  2,86,∆Āeen soodir…ďe laakara nguurndam aduna …ďe koynantaake lette …ďe ke…ďataa ballo
  2,87,Min ngaddanii Muusaa deftere nde …ďaawo makko Min ndewni heen nulaa…ďe Min ngaddani Iisaa …ďii Maryam la…ď…ďinale Min cemmbirini mo wonki tedduki mbela kala nde nulaa…óo addi he mon ko welaani pittaali mon mawnikino-…óon yoga heen njeddon …ďe yoga heen mbaron …ďe
  2,88,"∆Āe mbii …ďer…óe amen …óe ko uddii…óe, accu tan ko Alla hu…ói …ďe sabu keefeeru ma…ď…ďe, na fam…ói ko …ďe ngoon…óinta"
  2,89,"Nde deftere ari e ma…ď…ďe iwde e Alla, ende nuun…óina ko …ďe njogii ado …óuum …ďe ngonndoo ko wallitoraade …óum dow …ďeen yeddu…ďe nde ko …ďe nganndi ko ari he ma…ď…ďe …ďe njiddi …óum, yo ku…ódi Alla won e heefer…ďe"
  2,90,Bone woni e ko…ďe coodiri ko'e ma…ď…ďe nde …ďe njeddi -e too√Īe- ko Alla jippini Alla jippinta …ďural Makko dow mbo O welaa e jeyaa…ďe Mako …ďe kaandii e tikkere mawnde heefer…ďe …ďee na ke…ďa lette bon…óe
  2,91,"Si …ďe mbi'aama ngoon…óinee ko Alla jippini ko …ďe mbi'a min ngoon…óina ko jippinaa e amen …ďe njedda ko wonaa …óuum te ko …óuum woni goonga nuun…óin…óo ko …ďe njogii, wii …ďe ko wa…ói o…óon mbarannoo annabaa…ďe Alla …ďe so tawno o…óon ngoon…óini"
  2,92,Nde Muusaa addani on la…ď…ďinale njogiti-…óon ngaari ndi …ďaawo makko onon ko on too√Īoo…ďe
  2,93,"Min …ďami e mon fodoore Min …ďamti dow mon haayre Tuur ∆īettiree ko Min ngaddani on ko e semmbe nanee, …ďe mbii min nanii min ngoopi …ďer…óe mum en …óe keewi dak rewde ngaari ndi e keefeeru ma…ď…ďe, wii bone wonii e ko goon…óingol mon yamiri on so tawno o…óon ngoon…óini"
  2,94,Wii so tawii ko onon tan ke…ďata aljanna to laakara njelo…óee maayde so tawii ko on goon…óu…ďe
  2,95,∆Āe njelotaako …óum pooma e ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe ngardini Alla Ombo anndi too√Īoo…ďe …ďe
  2,96,Maa a taw ko kam…ďe …ďuri reer…óude e nguurndam e …ďeen renndin…ďe e Alla mbela gooto e ma…ď…ďe na yi…ói wuurde duu…ďe ujunere wuurde mbo ko juuti wo…ó…óintaa mo lette Alla Mo yi'a golle ma…ď…ďe
  2,97,Wii kala gon…óo ga√Īo Jibriil yo anndu ko kanko yottini Kur'aana nder …ďernde maa e yamiroore Alla nde nuun…óini defte …óe …ďe njogii ko nde peewal e malu goon…óin…ďe
  2,98,Kala gon…óo ga√Īo Alla e malaykaa…ďe Makko e nulaa…ďe Makko e Jibriil e Miika'il Alla dey ko ga√Īo heefer…ďe …ďe
  2,99,Min njippinii e maa maandeeji la…ď…ďinooji alaa jeddoowo …ói sonaa faasigee…ďe …ďe
  2,100,Wolla kala nde …ďe pi…ďi aadi wooda e ma…ď…ďe firtu…ďe mbo accu tan …ďur…ďe heewde e ma…ď…ďe ngoon…óinaani
  2,101,"Nde Nulaa…óo Alla ari e ma…ď…ďe ombo goon…óina ko …ďe njogii ko, woodi heen sete salii rontii deftere Alla nde wa'i no …ďe nganndaa nii"
  2,102,"∆Āe ndewi ko sey…óaneeji njannganta laamu Suleymaan Suleymaan yeddaani kono ko sey…óaneeji …ói njeddi e…ói nganndina yim…ďe mbilewu e ko jippina dow malaykaa…ďe …ói…óo to Baabil e Haaruut e Maaruu kala nde …ďe nganndini go…ó…óo …ďe mbi'a minen dey ko min fitina taa yeddu, …ďe jnnga e ma…ď…ďe no …ďe ceerndirta neddo e debbo mum, …ďe lorataa hay gooto sinaa e yamiroore Alla …ďe njannga ko bonnanta …ďe, …ďe nganndii kala battindir…óo …óum alaa ge…óal to laakara ko bone …ďe mbattiti ko'e ma…ď…ďe tawiino …ďe nganndi"
  2,103,Tawno …ďe ngoon…óinii …ďe kuli Alla ko mbarjaari immorde e Alla …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude
  2,104,"Onon goon…óin…ďe taa mbi'ee aynu min mbi'ee ndaar (fadir) min nanee, heefer…ďe …ďee na ke…ďa lette. muus…óe"
  2,105,"∆Āeen yim…ďe deftere yeddu…ďe e renndin…ďe e Alla nji…óataa jooma mon jippina e mon mo∆ī∆ī ere,Alla noon ko MboO welaa o wa…óanta yurmeend e Mum ko O jooma …ďural mawngal"
  2,106,Kala nde Min itti aaye maa momti mbo deen Min ngadda …ďur…óo mbo maa wano mbo mbela a anndaa Alla Mo waawi kala huunde
  2,107,Mbela a anndaa wonde ko Alla jeyi laamu asamaanji e lesdi on ngalaa keedanoowo mon wolla ballo sonaa Alla
  2,108,"Wolla nji…ó-…óon ko naamnaade nulaa…óo mon o wano Muusaa naamnoranoo ko adi,i kala mbo wattiti goon…óingol keefeeru tawa o majjii laawol peewngol"
  2,109,Heew…ďe e yim…ďe deftere nji…ói ruttude on heefer…ďe …ďaawo goon…óingol mon ko nga√Īgu pittaali mum en caggal nde …ďe laa…ďaa goonga o njaafee ngaccanon haa yamiroore Alla ara Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde
  2,110,√Ďii…ďnee juulde tottiree asakal kala mo∆ī∆īere nde mba…óan-…óon ko'e mon maa on tawnde to Alla ko Kanko Alla woni ji'oowo ko ngolloton
  2,111,"∆Āe mbii alaa naatoowo aljanna sonaa Yahuude maa nasaaraajo …óuum woni muuyaande ma…ď…ďe, wii: …ďe ngaddee daliil moo…óon so tawii ko on goon…óu…ďe"
  2,112,"Ko goonga kala mbo totti yeeso makko Alla o woni mo∆ī∆īini, ma o he…ó mbarjaari makko to joomum kulol alanaa …ďe …ďe cunotaako"
  2,113,"Yahuud en mbii nasaara en ngonaani e hay huunde nasaara en mbii yahuud en ngonaani e hay huunde, tawa e…ďe njannga deftere nde, ko noon …ďe nganndaa …ďe mbiinoo ko Alla √Īaawata luural hakkunde ma…ď…ďe √Īande darnga"
  2,114,"Hombo …ďuri too√Īe oon ka…óoowo yo innde Alla jante nder juulir…óe ombo daranii bonnude …óe …ďeen potaani naatde …óe so wonaa e kulol, …ďe ke…ďa koyeera e aduna …ďe ke…ďa lette maw…óe to laakara"
  2,115,"Fu…ónaange e hirnaange ko Alla woodani kala heen …óo kuccit, toon ko yeeso Alla, pellet Alla noon ko jaaj…óo e ganngal Makko piiltingal"
  2,116,"∆Āe mbii Alla Mo jogitii …ďi…ó…óo senaande woodanii Mo, nganndee kala ko woni e asamaanji e lesdi ko Kanko woodani fof na …óoftoo Mo"
  2,117,"Pu…ó…óu…óo asamaanji …ói e lesdi ndi, so O √Īaawii huunde O wi'ata …óum tan ko: won …óum wona"
  2,118,"∆Āe nganndaa …ďe mbi'a mbela Alla haaldataa min wolla O addana min maande, ko noon adinoo…ďe ma…ď…ďe mbiinoo …ďer…óe mum en nanndi goonga tigi Min la…ď…ďinii maandeeji …ói wonande yim…ďe yananaa…ďe …ďe"
  2,119,"Minen Min nelirii ma goonga ngonaa beltinoowo jeertinoowo, A naa…ďntaake ma yim…ďe jayngol Jahannama"
  2,120,Yahuud e nasaara en mbeletaake ma haa njokkaa laawol ma…ď…ďe yo a wii …ďe nganndee ko peewal Alla woni peewal so a jokkii belee…óe ma…ď…ďe …ďaawo nde ke…ď…óaa ganndal ndeen a da√Īataa ballal Alla
  2,121,"∆Āeen …ďe Min ngaddani deftere nde e…ďe nde njannga no haaniri ko …ďeen tigi ngoon…óini nde, kala mbo yeddi nde ko …ďeen tigi ngoni bonnoraa…ďe"
  2,122,"Onon …ďi…ď…ďe Isra'iil ciftoree mo∆ī∆īereeji Am …ói Mi wa…óani on, Miin tigi wa…ói mon …ďurir…óon winndere"
  2,123,"Kulee √Īande fittaandu alaa ko waawani fittandu wonndu te ndu ja…ďantaake coodtiigu kadi tefaneede nafataa ndu, …ďe ke…ďataa ballo"
  2,124,"Nde Alla humpitori Ibrahiima konngi o timmini …ói, O Wi'i: Miin Mi wa…óat ma gardotoo…óo yim…ďe …ďe Ibarahiima wi'i wa…ó …óum kadi e …ďesngu am O wi'i too√Īoo…ďe …ďe ke…ďataa fodoore Am"
  2,125,Nde Min mba…ói suudu ndu ruttorde yim…ďe e hoolaare njokito-…óee darnde Ibrahiima wona juulirde Min ngaadanii Ibrahiima e Ismaa'iila yo …ďe la…ď…ďin suudu Amngam wanngotoo…ďe e ufnotoo…ďe e juuloo…ďe
  2,126,Nde Ibrahiima wi'i jooma am wa…óan min nduu suudu leydi hoolniindi nje…óaa yim…ďe mum …ďi…ď…ďe le…ó…óe wonande goon…óin…ďe Alla e √Īande wattan O wi'i kala jeddu…óo Mi weltina mo see…óa fawoo heen Mi faana mon lette jayngol e battane bon…óe
  2,127,Nde Ibrahiima e Isma'iila …ďamtatnoo dos…óe suudu ndu e…ďe mbi'a Jooma amen ja…ďan min ko Aan woni nanoowo nganndu…óo fof
  2,128,Jooma amen wa…ó min ja…ďan…ďe Ma mba…óaa e …ďesngu amen le√Īol juul…ďe yo A hollu min tinndinor…óe dewe amen njaafo-∆äaa min ko Aan tigi woni jaafotoo…óo jurmotoo…óo
  2,129,"Jooma amen wa…ó e ma…ď…ďe nulaa…óo ombo janngana …ďe aayeeje Maa o anndina …ďe Kur'aana Maa o e sunna o, o la…ď…ďina …ďe ko Aaan tigi woni jaalii…óo √Īee√Ī…óu…óo"
  2,130,Alaa …óuurnotoo…óo (calotoo…óo) laawol Ibrahiima sonaa mbo fittaandu mum …óaayi nganndee Min cu…ďiima mo e aduna kanko o jeyaa ko e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe to laakara
  2,131,Nde Jooma mum wii Mo ja…ďanAm ngonaa juul…óo o wi'i mi ja…ďanii Jooma binnde …óe
  2,132,"Ibrahiima tinndini …ďi…ď…ďe mum, Yaakuub kadi wa…ói noon, onon …ďi…ď…ďe am Alla su…ďaniima on diine …óe taa maayee sonaa ko on juul…ďe"
  2,133,Mbela on ceediima nde maayde arani Yaakuuba nde o wii …ďi…ď…ďe mum …ďee holko ndewoton caggal am…ďe mbii min ndewan dewetee…óo maa e dewetee…óo baabiraa…ďe maa Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaak dewetee…óo gooto minen ko oon min njebbilanii
  2,134,"Ngool ko le√Īol jawtungol engol he…ďa ko ngol fagginoo, onon ne o…óon ke…ďa ko paggi-…óon on naamnetaake ko …ďe ngollatnoo"
  2,135,"Yahuud e Nasaara en mbii ngonee Yahuuda maa Nasaara ndeen peewon wii: -aan annabiijo- accu dey min ngonata ko e diine Ibrahiima peew…ó …óe o jeyanooka e sirku…ďe …ďe"
  2,136,Mbi'ee min ngoon…óinii Alla e ko jippinaa dow amen e ko jippinaa dow Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaak e Yaakuub e Asbaat e ko Muusaa e Iisaa okkaa e ko annabaa…ďe …ďee okka iwde e joomiraawo ma…ď…ďe min ceerndataa hay gooto e ma…ď…ďe ko kam…ďe min njebbilanii
  2,137,So tawii …ďe ngoon…óinii wano ko ngoon…óin-…óon ko ndeen tawa …ďe peewii so …ďe …óuurniima ndeen …ďe ngoni ko e luutndaade maa Alla suran ma …ďe ko Kanko woni nanoowo nganndu…óo fof
  2,138,"Diine Alla neesuyaŇčkooje alaa diine baa…óe no diine Alla …óe, minen ko Kanko min ndewata"
  2,139,"Wii mbela on njeddondirat e amen fii Alla te ko Kanko woni joomiroowo men, min ke…ďat golle amen ke…ďon golle mon minen ko Kanko min laa…ďanta"
  2,140,"Mbela on nji…ó wiide wonde Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaaka e Yaakuub e Asbaat …ďe ngonndoo ko yahudee…ďe maa nasaara…ďe, wii mbela ko onon …ďuri anndude Alla hol mbo …ďuri too√Īe oon cuu…óoowo seedanfaagu iwde e Alla, Alla noon yeebotaako ko …ďe ngollata ko"
  2,141,"Ngool ko le√Īol jawtungol engol he…ďa ko ngol, fagginoo onon ne o…óon ke…ďa ko paggi-…óon on naamnetaake ko …ďe ngollatnoo"
  2,142,"Arma ka …ďe fuyunngaa…ďe e yim…ďe mbi'a: \"E ko hucciŇčtini …ďe ga'e Qibla ma…ď…ďe mo …ďe laatinoo e mu'un?\" Maaku: \"Ko Alla Woodani fu…ónaange e hiirnaange, Himo Fewnira on Mo O Muuyi faade laawol focciingol"
  2,143,"Ko wano nii Men wa…óiri on mofte hakindii…óe fii yo on laato seedoytoo…ďe e dow yim…ďe …ďen, Nulaa…óo on seeditoyoo e dow mo'on. Men wa…óiraa oo Qibla mo fewtataa e mu'un si wanaa no Men anndira on jokkoowo Nulaa…óo on e on ruttotoo…óo batte bonnere mu'un, hay si tawii …óum laatike ko sattu-…óum, si wanaa e dow …ďen …ďe Allah fewni. Allah Laatoraali yeeboowo liimanaaku mo'on: Pellet, Allah ko Hilnotoo…óo yim…ďe …ďen Yurmee …ďe"
  2,144,"Gom…óii Me…óen Reeni waylitorgol yeeso maa ngon ka kammu. Ma Men Fewtinire Qibla waalaŇčtoo…óo ma:Fewtinir yeeso maa…óa ngon baŇčŇče Juulirde HoormaŇčteere nden.Nokku kala ko ngo…óon,fewtiniree geece mon …óen baŇčŇče mayru:Pellet,…ďen Rokkaa…ďe Defte …ďen no anndi [Al Qur'aanaare nden] ko nde goonga immorde ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe,Allah non siforaali Welsinsii…óo e ko …ďe gollata"
  2,145,"Mi Woondii si a addanii …ďen rokkaa…ďe deftere nden kala maande,…ďe jokkataa Qibla maa on,a wonaa jokkoowo Qibla ma…ď…ďe on,yoga e ma…ď…ďe wonaali jokkoo…ďe Qibla yoga.Mi Woondii si a jokkii m…ďelee…óe maa…ďe …ďaawo kon ko ari e maa e anndal,pellet,an ontuma a jeyaama e too√Īu…ďe …ďen"
  2,146,"∆Āen …ďe Men Rokki Deftere nden hi…ďe nganndiri …óum wano …ďe nganndiri …ďi…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe; pellete, fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe hino suu…óude goonga kan hara hi…ďe nganndi"
  2,147,"Goonga kan ko ko ummori ko Joomi maa, wata a laatodu e …ďen sikkitii…ďe"
  2,148,"Ena woodani mo kala baŇčŇče …óe o fewtata e mun.Adondiree e mo∆ī∆īereeji,nokku kala ka laati-…óon,Allah artiray on,on denndaangal. Pellete,Allah ko hattan…óo e dow kala huunde"
  2,149,"Nokku kala ka yaltir…óaa, fewtinir yeeso maa ngon baŇčŇče Suudu Hormorteendu ndun, pellet, …óum ko goonga ummoraade Joomi maa, Allah Wonaali Welsindii…óo e kon ko gollo-ton"
  2,150,"Nokku kala ka yaltir…óaa, fewtinir yeeso maa ngon baŇčŇče Suudu Hormorteendu ndun, nokku kala ka ngon…óon, fewtiniree geece mon …óen baŇčŇče mayru fii wata wonan yim…ďe …ďen hujja e hoore mo'on - so wanaa …ďen too√Īu…ďe e ma…ď…ďe. Wata non on hulu…ďe, Hulee Lam, fii no Mi Timminira neema Am On e mo'on, belajo'o on feeway"
  2,151,"Wano no Men Nuliri non e mo'on Nulaa…óo ummoraade e mo'on,Himo janngana on Aayeeje Amen,himo la…ď…ďina on,himo anndina on Deftere nden,o anndina on ko on anndaana"
  2,152,"JaŇčtee Lam, Mi Anndita on; jaarnee Lam wata on yeddam"
  2,153,"Ko onon yo …ďen gom…óim…ďe, wallitoree mu√Ī√Īaare e juulde. Pellet, Allah Hino Wonndi e mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen"
  2,154,"Wata on wi'an …ďen wariraa…ďe fii Allah …ďen: \"ko …ďe maay…ďe\". Ko woni, …ďen ko wuur…ďe, kono on so'aa anndude"
  2,155,"Ma Men jaribo on huunde, immorde e kulol, e heege, e …óuytagol jawle, e woŇčkiiji, e dim…óe; Wewlin mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen"
  2,156,"∆Āen taw…ďe si masiibo he…ďii…ďe, …ďe wi'a: \"Menen dey ko Allah jeyi men, pellet to Makko menruttortoo"
  2,157,"∆Āen …óon, hino e dow ma…ď…ďe toraaje e yurmeende ummoraade ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe, ko kam…ďe ngoni feewu…ďe …ďen"
  2,158,"Pellet,Safaa e Marwa ko jeyaa…óe e maandeeji [diine] Allah.Kala on hajju…óo ka suudu [Kaaba], maa o wa…ói Umra,ella woo fawaaki mo nde o wanngotoo hakkunde majji.On mo gattii mo∆ī∆īere,pellet Allah ko Jaarnoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,159,"Pellet, …ďen suudoo…ďe kon ko Men Jippini immorde e …ďanngannduyeeji e peewal, …ďaawo nde Men ∆Āannginani …óum yim…ďe …ďen ka Deftere, …ďen …óon, Allah ena Hu…óude …ďe, hu…óoo…ďe …ďen na hu…óude …ďe"
  2,160,"Si wanaa …ďen tuubu…ďe …ďe mo∆ī∆īini …ďe …ďaŇčngini: Mi Ja…ďanay …ďen …óon tuubuubuyee, ko Min Woni Ja…ďoowo tuubuubuyee Huu…ďu…óo-yurmeende"
  2,161,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďe maayi ko …ďe heereraa…ďe, …ďen …óon ena fawii…ďe kuddi Allah ndin e Malaa'ika en e yim…ďe …ďen denndaangal"
  2,162,"Ko …ďe luttoo…ďe e magge. ∆Āe hayfinaŇčtaake le…ďte …óen, …ďe wonaali nennanaŇčtee…ďe"
  2,163,"Rewetee…óe mon On ko Rewetee…óe Gooto. Rewetee…óo Alaa tanaa Makko, Jurmotoo…óo Yurmeende heeriinde e nde heeraaki Yurmeende"
  2,164,"Pellet hino e ndeer tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e luutondiral jemma e √Īalorma on, e le…ó…óe dogirooje …óen ka bahru nafugol yim…ďe …ďen, e kon ko Allah Jippiniri ka kammu, immorde e ndiyam, O Wurniri …óum leydi ndin …ďaawo maayugol mayri O Saakti e mayri kala daaba, e waylitugol keneeli …óin e duule eltaa…óe …óen hakkunde leydi e kammu, maandeeji wonannde yim…ďe haqqiloo…ďe"
  2,165,"Hino e yim…ďe njogitii…ďe ko woori Allah yerondir…ói, hi…ďe nji…óira…ói wano Allah yi…óirtee, [ko] …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďuri sa…ótude giggol wonande Allah. Hara …ďen too√Īu…ďe annduno tuma …ďe nji'oyta lepte …óen, wonde doole …óen fof ko Allah heeranii, e wonde Allah ko Sa…ótu…óo lepte"
  2,166,"Tuma nde hisnii jokkanoo…ďe …ďen pottitoyii jokkunoo…ďe …ďen, …ďe nji'a lepte …óen, sabuuji …óin ta∆īira …ďe"
  2,167,"Jokkunoo…ďe …ďen mbi'a: \"Hara nun fehre ruttagol no woodannoo men, men pottitora …ďe wano …ďe pottitori men nii\". Ko wano nii Allah Hollirta …ďe golleeji ma…ď…ďe …óin; hayrere e dow ma…ď…ďe, …ďe ngonaali njaltoo…ďe e yiite ngen"
  2,168,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe! √Ďaamee yoga e ko woni ka leydi ko dagii ko laa…ďi, wata on jokku juri=taabe seytaane …óin : Pellet, ko o ga√Īo mo'on fee√Īu…óo"
  2,169,"Anndee ko o yamirta on ko bone e paŇčkare, e nde wowloton e hoore Allah ko on anndaa"
  2,170,"Si …ďe wi'anaa:\"Jokkee kon ko Allah Jippini\", …ďe mbi'a:\"Ko woni, men njokkay ko men tawri kon baabiraa…ďe amen\";e hay si baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen haqqilataa hay e huunde …ďe haanditaaki"
  2,171,"Misal …ďen yeddu…ďe hino wa'i wa on ewnotoo…óo kon ko nanataa si wanaa noddaandu e ewnal. Ko faa…óu…ói, mumi…óu…ói, wumu…ói; kaŇčji …ói haqqiltaa"
  2,172,"Ko onon yo …ďen gom…óim…ďe! √Ďamee immorde e laa…ďu…ói …ói Men Arsiki on, jaarnon Allah si on wonii ko KaŇčko rewoton"
  2,173,"Anndee ko O Harminani on, ko jii…ďe, e ∆īii∆īam, e teewu kose, e [huunde hirsiraande] daginiraande ko woori Allah. Kala on du√Īaa…óo [e √Īaamugol …óum] hara wanaa …ďew…óo wanaa jaggitu…óo, bakkatu fawaaki mo. Pellet Allah ko Ya'fotoo…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  2,174,"Pellet …ďen suu…óoo…ďe ko Allah Jippini kon e Deftere nden, hi…ďe soodira …óum cogguwel fam…óungel. ∆Āen …óon alaa wa…óude ka deedi ma…ď…ďe si wanaa yiite ngen; Allah Yeewtidtaa …ďe √Īalnde darngal, O La…ď…ďiŇčtaa …ďe, hino woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe"
  2,175,"Ko …ďen ngoni soodir…ďe majjere nden peewal, e lepte …óen ya'fuyee. kaawse ko mu√Ī√Īori…ďe ka yiite"
  2,176,"∆äuum noon, ko fii Allah Jippinirii Deftere nden goonga. pellet …ďen luutondir…ďe e Deftere nden …ďe ngonii e lurral wo…ó…óungal"
  2,177,"Dewal ngal wonaali fewtiŇčgol geece mon …óen …ďaŇčnge fu…ónaange e hiirnaange. Ko woni tun dewal ngal: ko on gom…óin…óo Alla e √Ďalaande sakkitiinde nden, e Malaa'ika en, e Deftere nden, e Annabaa…ďe …ďen; o okki jawdi -e hoore yi…óugol ndi- joomiraa…ďe …ďadondiral, e wondu…ďe …ďen, e …ďillii…ďe …ďen, e …ďii hoore-laawol, e …ďen torotoo…ďe, e fii rin…óinngol daa…óe; o nii…ďni juulde, o totti asakal, e …ďen hunnoo…ďe aadondiral ma…ď…ďe si …ďe haldidaama, e …ďen mu√Ī√Īitoo…ďe ka baasi e ka lorra, e fewndo gowole. Ko …ďen ngoni goongu…ďe …ďen, ko …ďen kadi ngoni gom…óu…ďe"
  2,178,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe,njottiigu farlaama e mo'on:dimo sabu dimo, jeyaa…óo sabu jeyaa…óo,deyel sabu deyel.Kala ya'fanaa…óo go…ó…óum e musi…ó…óo makko,ko jokkitirogol no mo∆ī∆īiri tottira e makko no mo∆ī∆īiri.∆äum …óoo ko hoynaneede immorde e Joomi mo'on e yurmeende.Kala on jaggitu…óo …ďaawo …óu'um,no woodani mo lepte muusu…óe"
  2,179,"No woodani on ka njottiigu nguurdam, yo joomiraa…ďe haqqilaaji. Belajo'o on wonay gom…óu…ďe"
  2,180,"Farlaama e mo'on:si maayde nden arii e mo'on,si o accii jawle: wasiyanagol jibin…ďe mo …ďen,e …ďadondiraa…ďe …ďen no mo∆ī∆īiri.Ko hannduyee e dow gom…óu…ďe …ďen"
  2,181,"Kala on waylitu…óo …óum …ďaawo o nannde, pellet bakkaatu mun on ko …ďen waylitu…ďe fawii. Allah ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,182,"On mo huli oo√Īaare immorde e wasiyii…óo maa bakkaatu o mo∆ī∆īini hakkunde ma…ď…ďe,bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Pellet Alla ko Yawtanoowo Yurmotoo…óo"
  2,183,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, koorka kan farlaama e mo'on wano ka farliranoo e …ďen adinoo…ďe on, …ďelajo'o laato…óon gom…óu…ďe"
  2,184,"√Ďal…ói limtaa…ói. Kala e mo'on laatii…óo nawnu…óo maa e hoore-jahal: ko limtugol √Īal…ói goo. No fawii …ďen ha…ótan…ďe ka, √Īammingol …ďilii…óo. Kala on gattu…óo mo∆ī∆īere …óum no mo∆ī∆īani mo. Ko nde hooroton …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on, si wonii hi…óon nganndi"
  2,185,"Lewru koorka ndun, ndu Alqur'aanaare nden jippinaa e mu'un, ko ndu peewal wonannde yim…ďe …ďen e …ďangannduyeeji immorde e peewal e serndugol. On e mo'on seedii…óo lewru ndun, yo o hooru ndu. On taw…óo no nawni maa himo e hoore-jahal, ko limtugol e √Īal…ói goo. Alla no Faandanii on neweende O Faandanaaki on sa…óteende; e fii yo on timmin limoore nden e no mawniniro Alla kon ko O Fewni on, belajo'o on jaarnay Mo"
  2,186,"Si jeyaa…ďe Am …ďen lamndike lan fii Am, hary Min: Ko Mi ∆Āa…óii…óo. Mi…óo Jaabina toraare torotoo…óo si o torike Lam. Yo …ďe nooto Lam, e yo …ďe gom…óinam, belajo'o …ďe feeway"
  2,187,"Daginanaama on jemma koorka kan yiidugol e rew…ďe mon …ďen. Ko …ďe koltu mo'on ko on koltu ma…ď…ďe. Alla Anndii wonde on laatinoke jaŇčfotoo…ďe ko*e-mon,O Ja…ďani on tuubuubuyee O Ya'fii on.Jooni non,soccondiree e ma…ď…ďe …óa…ď…ďon ko Alla Winndani on.√Ďaamee yaron haa gaarawol danewol ngol …ďaŇčngirana on …ďalewol ngol ka peeral, refti timminiron koorka kan jemma. Wata on soccondir e ma…ď…ďe hara ko on ufnii…ďe ka juulir…óe.∆äum ko keeri Allah, wata on …ďa…óto …ói.Ko wano nii Allaahu On ∆ĀaŇčnginiraŇčta yim…ďe …ďen aayeeje Makko …óen,belajo'o …ďe wona gom…óu…ďe"
  2,188,"Wata on √Īaamir jawle mon …óen hakkundeeji mo'on e hoore mehre, werloron …óe e √Īaawoo…ďe …ďen fii yo fedde goo √Īaamira e jawle yim…ďe …ďen bakkaatu, hara hi…óon nganndi"
  2,189,"Hi…ďe naamno-maa fii daror…óe lebbi, wi'u: \"∆äin ko waqaŇčtinanay…ói yim…ďe e fii hajju\".Dewal ngal wonaali nde ngardaŇčton cuu…ói …óin immorde ka …ďabbe majji, si ko woni dewal ngal: ko on gom…óu…óo.Ngardanee cuu…ói …óin ka dame majji.Hulon Allah,belajo'o on malete"
  2,190,"Ha…ďee fii laawol Alla ngol …ďen ha…ďoo…ďe on, wata on jaggitu. Pellet, Alla yi…óaa jaggitoo…ďe …ďen"
  2,191,"waree…ďe nokku kala ka taw…óon …ďe, yaltinee…ďe nokku ka …ďe yaltiniri on: ko geddi …óin …ďuri mawnude e dii ha…ďugol ngol. Wata on ha…ďu…ďe ka Misiide HormaŇčteere haa …ďe ha…ďa on e mayre. Si …ďe ha…ďii on ha…ďee …ďe. Ko wano nii woni njo…ďdi heefer…ďe …ďen"
  2,192,"Si …ďe ha…óitike, pellet, Alla ko O Hafroowo Huu…ďu…óo-yumeende"
  2,193,"Ha…ďee …ďe haa nokku ka laatotaako fitina, diina kan laatanoo Alla. Si …ďe ha…óitike, haray jaggitere alanaa si wanaa …ďen too√Īoo…ďe"
  2,194,"Si …ďe ha…ďii on e lewru hormaŇčteeru, ha…ďee …ďe e lewru hormaŇčteeru, horminaa…ói …óin ko yottondirtee …óum. On mo jaggiti e mo'on jaggitee e dow makko yeru kon ko o jaggiti e dow moo…óon. Hulee Alla anndon pellet Alla no wonndi …ďen gom…óu…ďe"
  2,195,"WiŇčtee e fii laawol Alla, wata on bugor juu…óe mon …óen faade e halakuyee. Mo∆ī∆īinee, pellet Alla no Yi…ói mo∆ī∆īinay…ďe …ďen"
  2,196,"Timminiree hajju ngun e 'omra on fii Alla. Si on sakkaama: fawike on ittugol kon ko newii e kirse, wata on femmbu ko'e mon …óen haa kirse …óen yottoo nokku majje. On taw…óo e mo'on ko √Īaw…óo maa lorra no ka hoore makko, ko soktorgol: koorka, maa sadaqa maa dammol. Si on wonii e hoolaare, on mo dakmitori 'omra on haa ka hajju: fawike mo ittugol kon ko newii e kirse. Mo he…ďaali, ko hoorugol bal…óe tati ka hajju e jee…ói…ói si on ruttike; …óen ko sappo timmu…óe. Ko jaŇčtaa koo, ko fii on taw…óo …ďeynguure mun nden laataaki ho…óu…ďe ka Misiide hormaŇčte. Hulee Alla, anndon pellet Alla ko sa…ótu…óo lepte"
  2,197,"Hajju ngun:ko lebbi anndaa…ói. Mo anniyike e nder majji hajju,renndugol alaa,wanaa faasoqingol wanaa kadi yeddondiro ka hajju.Kala ku gollug…óon e mo∆ī∆īere, Allah no Anndi …óum.Yoo…ďee,ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e njoo…ďa,ko gom…óal. Hulee Lam yo joomiraa…ďe haqqillaaji"
  2,198,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde …óa…ď…ďoton arsike immorde e Joomi mo'on. Si on iwtii 'Aarafaat, JaŇčtee innde Alla ka nokku horminannde. JaŇčtoron Mo wano O fewniri on non, hari on laatinoke ado muu…óum ko on jeyaa…ďe e majju…ďe"
  2,199,"Refti yahron ka yim…ďe …ďen yahri …óon, Insinano…óon Alla. Pellet Alla ko Yaafotoo…óo Huu…ďu…óo-yurmeende"
  2,200,"Si on gaynii dewe hajju mon ngun, jaŇčtoree innde Alla wano jaŇčtorton baabiraa…ďe mo'on, maa ko …ďuri …óum tii…óude. No e yim…ďe …ďen wi'oo…ďe: \"Joomi amen Rokku men ka aduna\", alanaa mo ka laakara ge…ďal-mo∆ī∆īal"
  2,201,"No e ma…ď…ďe wi'oo…ďe: Joomi amen, okku min moyyere aduna e laakara, ndanndaa min lebte jayngol"
  2,202,"∆Āen …óon, no woodani …ďe ge…ďal-mo∆ī∆īal e kon ko …ďe faggitii. Alla ko Yaawu…óo hasboore"
  2,203,"JaŇčtee Innde Alla e √Īal…ói limtaa…ói. On yaccin…óo e nder bal…óe …ói…ói, bakkaatu fawaaki mo; on ne…ďtin…óo kadi, bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Wonannde on gom…óu…óo. Hulee Alla, nganndon pellet ko ka Makko moo…ďindiroyte-…óon"
  2,204,"No e yim…ďe …ďen on mo konngol mun no haawne ka nguurdam aduna, himo seediŇčtina Alla kon ko woni e ndeer …ďernde makko, hara non ko kaŇčko …ďuri sa…ótude wennje"
  2,205,"Si o huccitii, o yaha ka leydi fii o bonnu e mayri, o halka gese e ge√Ī√Īi. Alla Yi…óaa bononda"
  2,206,"Si o wi'anaama: \"Hulu Alla\", mawniŇčtinaare he…ďa mo sabu bakkaatu. Jahannama yonii mo, e nge bonii nda…ó…óudi"
  2,207,"No e yim…ďe …ďen: on mo no soo…ótira woŇčkii mun kin …óa…ď…ďugol yarluyee Alla. Alla ko Hilnotoo…óo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen"
  2,208,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, naatiree e lislaamu ka denndanngal, wata on jokku juri seytaane …óin. On ko ga√Īo moo…óon …ďaŇčngu…óo"
  2,209,"Si on oo√Īike …ďaawo koo ko ari on e …ďaŇčngannduyeeji, nganndee pellet, Alla ko Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  2,210,"Taw si …ďee no sabbii: si wanaa nde Allaahu On ArdaŇčta …ďe e ndeer ni…ďe duule wondude e Maalaa'ika en; fiyaaku gasinee. Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde fiyakuuji …óin"
  2,211,"Naamno ge…óal…ďe Israa'iila en:ko jelu woni ko Men Rokki …ďe e maandeeji …ďaŇčngu…ói! Kala wa…ótitu…óo neema Alla on …ďaawo on arude mo, pellet, Alla ko Tii…óu…óo lepte"
  2,212,"Nguurdam aduna …óam cu…óinanaama …ďeya heefer…ďe, hi…ďe jalkita …ďen gom…óim…ďe. ∆Āen gom…óu…ďe wonoyay dow ma…ď…ďe √Īalnde darngal. Alla no Arsikira on Mo O Muuyi, ko aldaa e hasboore"
  2,213,"Yim…ďe …ďen laatino mofte goote. Allaahu On Nuli Annabaa…ďe …ďen, wewlinoo…ďe e jeertinoo…ďe, O Jippindini e ma…ď…ďe Deftere nden hoore goonga, fii yo o √Īaawu hakkunde yim…ďe …ďen kon ko …ďe luuondiri e muu…óum. Luutondiraali e muu…óum, si wanaa …ďen rokkaa…ďe nde, …ďaawo kon ko ari …ďe e …ďaŇčngannduyeeji; ka bewre hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Allah Fewniri duŇčyee Makko …ďen gom…óim…ďe e kon ko …ďe luutondiri e muu…óum, immorde e goonga. Alla No Fewna on Mo O Muuyi, faade e laawol focciingol"
  2,214,"Kaa on sikku on naatay aljanna hara araali on sugu kon ko arunoo …ďen wulii…ďe on? He…ďiino …ďen sa…ótteende e lorra, …ďe dillinaa haa Nulaa…óo wi'i, e …ďen gom…óindim…ďe e makko: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ballal Alla ngal?\", hey, pellte ballal Alla ngal …ďa…ótiingal"
  2,215,"∆Āe ngaray naamnaade ma ko hon…óum …ďe sakkotoo, wi'u: \"Si won ko sakki…óon e mo∆ī∆īere, ko fii jibin…ďe on, e …ďadondiraa…ďe …ďen, e wondu…ďe …ďen, e …ďilii…ďe …ďen, e setee…ďe …ďen. kalako gollu…óon e mo∆ī∆īere, pellet Alla ko Anndu…óo …óum"
  2,216,"Hare nden farlaama e mo'on; nden non ko a√Īaande e mo'on,no tijjaa ka a√Īoton huunde hara ko nde mo∆ī∆īere mon, no tijjaa kadi ka yi…óoton huunde hara ko nde bone mon. Ko Alla No Anndi onon on nganndaa"
  2,217,"Hi…ďe naamno maa fii lewru hormaŇčte ndun, ha…ďugol e mayru, maaku: \"Ha…ďugol e mayru ko mawnu-…óum. Ko sakkagol e laawol Alla ngol e yeddugol Mo e Misiide hormorde nden e yaltingol yim…ďe mayre …ďen e mayre, …ďuri mawnude ka Alla. Ko shirku on kadi …ďuri mawnude dii wargol ngol; …ďe seerataa hi…ďe ha…ďa on haa …ďe rutta on e diina mon, si …ďe haa…ótanii. Kala e mo'on yaltondir…óo e diina mu'un, o maayi ko o keefeero: …ďen …óon, golle ma…ď…ďe …óen bonii aduna e laakara; ko …ďen ngoni yim…ďe yiite, …ďen ko luttoo…ďe ton"
  2,218,"Pellet, …ďen gom…óim…ďe e …ďen feru…ďe ha…ďiri fii laawol Alla, …ďen …óon no jortii Yurmeende Alla; Alla ko Ya'fotoo…óo Huu…ďu…óo-yurmeende"
  2,219,"Hi…ďe naamno-maa fi sanngara e karte, maaku: \"No e …óin …ói…ói bakkaatu maw…óo e nafawoy wonannde yim…ďe …ďen, ko bakkaatu majji on non …ďuri mawnude e dii nafawoy majji on\". Hi…ďe naamno-maa kadi hol ko …ďe sakkotoo? Maaku: \"yaafuya=Ko fawi e haaju\". Ko wano nii Alla ∆ĀaŇčnginiraŇčta on Aayeeje …óen, belajo'o on miijitoto"
  2,220,"Fii aduna on e laakara on, hi…ďe naamno-maa fii wondu…ďe …ďen, maaku: \"Ko mo∆ī∆īagol e ma…ď…ďe …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude\". Si on jillondirii e ma…ď…ďe, ko musi…ó…ďe mo'on. Alla no Anndi on mo∆ī∆īinoowo e on bonnoowo. Si Alla muuyuno, O ∆Āi…ótinanayno on. Pellet Alla ko Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  2,221,"Wata on resu …ďen rew…ďe shirkay…ďe haa …ďe gom…óina: Mi Woondii ko kor…óo gom…óin…óo …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude debbo shirkoowo hay si o haawnii on. Wata on resin …ďen wor…ďe shirkoo…ďe haa …ďe gom…óina: Mi Woondii ko maccu…óo gom…óin…óo …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude dimo shirkoowo hay si o haawnii on.∆Āen …óon hi…ďe nodda faade e yiite, Alla No Noddude e Aljanna e haforanal, e duŇčyee Makko. Himo ∆ĀaŇčngina Aayeeje Makko …óen wonannde yim…ďe …ďen, belajo'o …ďe wa'ajitoto"
  2,222,"Hi…ďe naam-no maa fii fiilordu, maaku: ∆äum ko nefinii …óum; luncitee rew…ďe …ďen fewndo fiilordu, wata on …ďa…óto …ďe haa …ďe laa…ďa. Si …ďe laa…ďii, ngaree e ma…ď…ďe nokku ka Alla Yamiri on …óon. Pellet Alla No Yi…ói tuubaya…ďe …ďen Himo Yi…ói kadi …ďen la…ď…ďinotoo…ďe"
  2,223,"Rew…ďe mon …ďen ko gese mo'on. Ngardee e ngesa mon mbam nokku kala ka faalira…óon, ngardinanee woŇčkiiji mon …óin. Hulle Alla, nganndon ko on kawroo…ďe e Makko. Weltin gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  2,224,"Wata on wa…óu Alla heedo fii ngoondooje mon …óen; nde …óiggoton, gom…óon hulon mo∆ī∆īinon hakkunde yim…ďe …ďen. Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,225,"Alla Nanngitirtaa on gardambi=bolle mehre ka ngoondooje mo'on, kono Himo Nanngitira on kon ko …ďer…óe mon …óen faggitii. Alla ko Hafroowo Mu√Ī√Īii…óo"
  2,226,"No woodani …ďen woondiroo…ďe suddii…ďe mun …ďen: habbitagol lebbi nayi. Si …ďe ruttike, pellet Alla ko Haforoowo Huu…ďu…óo-yurmeende"
  2,227,"Si …ďe fellitii ceergal ngal, pellet Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,228,"Seeraa…ďe …ďen yo habbiŇčtin ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óen laa…ďe tati; dagaŇčtaako …ďe suu…óugol kon ko Alla Tagi ka ndeer renngaaji ma…ď…ďe, si wonii hi…ďe gom…óim…ďe Alla e √Īalaande sakkitiinde. Ko moodi…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe jojjidi ruttugol …ďe e …óum, si hawrii hi…ďe faalaa weldital. No woodani …ďen [rew…ďe] yeru kon ko fawii…ďe, no mo∆ī∆īiri. No woodani wor…ďe …ďen: …ďural e dow ma…ď…ďe. Alla ko Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  2,229,"Ceergal, ko laa…ďi …ói…ó: ko jogitorgol no mo∆ī∆īiri maa accitira no mo∆ī∆īiri. DagaŇčtaako on ∆īettitugol huunde e kon ko rokku-…óon …ďe, si wanaa hara …ďe hulii [kam…ďe …ói…óo] nde …ďe nii…ďnataa keeri Alla …óin. Si on hulii roŇčkude √Īii…ďnude keeri Alla …óin, goopi alanaa …ďe e kon ko debbo on soktori. ∆äin ko keeri Alla, wata on jaggitu-…ói. kala jaggitu…óo keeri Alla …óin, ko …ďen ngoni too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  2,230,"Si o seerii mo, on [debbo] dagitaŇčtaako mo …ďaawo …óu'um, haa o resindira e gorko goo. Si on [gorko] seerii mo, goopi fawaaki …ďe nde …ďe ruttondira, si …ďe fellitii √Īii…ďnugol keeri Alla …óin.∆äin ko keeri Allah, Himo ∆ĀaŇčnginana …ói …ďen yim…ďe nganndu…ďe"
  2,231,"Si on seerii rew…ďe …ďen, laje ma…ď…ďe …óen yottike: jogitoree-…ďe no mo∆ī∆īiri maa accitoron …ďe no mo∆ī∆īiri. Wata on jogitor …ďe lorrugol nde jaggitoton. Kala wa…óu…óo …óum, gom…óii o too√Īii hoore-makko. Wata on jogitor Aayeeje Alla …óen jalnori. Annditee neemaaji Alla …ói O Neemini e mo'on, e ko O Jippini e mo'on immorde e Deftere e √Ďee√Īal; Himo Wa'ajora …óum. Hulle Alla, nganndon pellet Alla ko Anndu…óo kala huunde"
  2,232,"Si on seerii rew…ďe …ďen, laje ma…ď…ďe …óen yottike, wata on laagu …ďe nde moodi…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen resata …ďe; si …ďe welondirii hakkunde ma…ď…ďe no mo∆ī∆īiri. ∆äum no waajoree on taw…óo e mo'on no gom…óini Alla e √Ďalaande Sakkitiinde. Ko jaŇčtana…óon koo …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on, …ďuri laa…ďaande. Alla No Anndi onon on nganndaa"
  2,233,"Jibim…ďe …ďen yo muynin …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen duu…ďi …ói…ói timmu…ói; wonannde on faandii…óo timminde muyninngol ngol.No fawii jibinanaa…óo on, √Īammingol holitinira [rew…ďe] …ďen no mo∆ī∆īiri. WoŇčkii woo fawaaka si wanaa ko ki waawata. Wata jibin…óo on lorrire sabu …ďi…ó…óo makko on, wanaa jibinanaa…óo on kadi lorrirtee sabu …ďi…ó…óo makko on; no fawii ronoowo on yeru …óum. Si …ďe faandike entude e hoore yarlondiral hakkunde ma…ď…ďe e diisondiral, bakkaatu fawaaki …ďe. Si on faandike …óa…ď…ďude muyninanoowo on …ďi…ó…ďe mon …ďen, bakkaatu fawaakii on, si on jonnirii kon ko …ďen [muyninoo…ďe] hanndi e mo∆ī∆īere.Hulee Alla, nganndon ko O Reenu…óo kala ko golloton"
  2,234,"∆Āen maayoo…ďe e mo'on …ďe acca suddii…ďe: yo …ďen habbiŇčtin ko'e ma…ď…ďe lebbi nayi e bal…óe sappo. Si …ďe yottike laje ma…ď…ďe …óen, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko …ďe wa…óani ko'e ma…ď…ďe no mo∆ī∆īiri. Alla Ko Humpitii…óo kon ko golloton"
  2,235,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko wee…ďitoton, e sabboyde suddii…ďe …ďen, maa suu…óu…óon …óum ka woŇčkiiji mo'on. Alla No Anndi aray ka annditon fii ma…ď…ďe, ko woni tun, wata on fodondir e ma…ď…ďe [desal] e gunndoo: si wanaa nde wowloton koŇčngol mo∆ī∆īol, wata on fellitu humugol dewgal ngal haa lajal edda ngal yottoo. Ngande pellet Alla No Anndi ko woni e woŇčkiiji mo'on, ReŇčtee e Makko, nganndon pellet Alla Ko Haforoowo Mu√Ī√Īii…óo"
  2,236,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on si on seerii suddii…ďe …ďen ado on renndude e ma…ď…ďe maa jaŇčtanagol …ďe teŇče, dakmitee …ďe:no fawii galo on yeru makko, no fawii kadi baydoolo on yeru makko.Dakmitirgol …ďe no mo∆ī∆īiri.Hannduyee fawii…óo mo∆īim…ďe …ďen"
  2,237,"Si on seerii suddii…ďe …ďen ado on meemude …ďe, tawa on jaŇčtanike …ďe teŇče: ko feccere kon ko jaŇčti-…óon, si wanaa hara …ďe ya'afi maa on mo dewgal woni e juu…óe mu'un ya'afii. Ko nde ya'afoto…óon …ďurata …ďa…ótinnde gom…óal. Wata on yejjitu …ďural ngal hakkunde mo'on. pellet Alla ko Reenu…óo kala ko golloton"
  2,238,"Reenee e jul…óe …óen, e julde hakkundeere nden. Darano…óon Alla ko o to∆ī∆īinii…ďe"
  2,239,"Si on hulii, juulee ko on seppay…ďe maa wa…ó…óii…ďe. Si on hoolike, jaŇčtee Innde Alla nden wano O Anndiniri on kon ko on nganndaano"
  2,240,"∆Āen maayoo…ďe e mo'on …ďe acca suddii…ďe: ko wasiyanagol suddii…ďe …ďen dakmitor…óum haa hitaande nden timma, ko aldaa e yaltiŇčgol …ďe. Si …ďe yaltii, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko …ďe wa…óani ko'e ma…ď…ďe e mo∆ī∆īere. Alla ko Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  2,241,"No woodani …ďen seeraa…ďe: dakamitorgol no mo∆ī∆īiri. ko goongofawii…óo gom…óu…ďe …ďen"
  2,242,"Ko wano nii Alla ∆ĀaŇčnginiraŇčta on Aayeeje Makko …óen, belajo'o on haqqilay"
  2,243,"E a tinaali …ďen njaltunoo…ďe e galleeji mu'un, kam…ďe ko …ďe guluuje, ka reenagol e maayde, Allaahu On Daalani …ďe: \"Maayee\", refti O Wuurniti …ďe? Pellet Alla ko Jom ∆Āural e dow yim…ďe …ďen, ko woni tun, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen njaanataa [Alla]"
  2,244,"Ha…ďee fii laawol Alla Ngol, nagndon pellet Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,245,"Ko hombo woni on √Īawloowo Alla √Īamaande mo∆ī∆īere, O Sowitana mo nde cowalle …óuu…óu…óe? Alla No ∆Āi…óttina Himo Ya√Ī√Īa, ko faade ka Makko ruttete-…óon"
  2,246,"E a tinaali ngun mbatu …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'ila, …ďaawo Muusaa, tuma nde …ďe wi'annoo Annabaajo ma…ď…ďe on: \"Imminan men lam…óo, men ha…ďa fii laawol Alla Ngol?\" O maaki: \"Hara on tijjaaki si hare nden farlaama e mo'on nde roŇčkoton ha…ďude?\" …ďe mbi'i: \"Ko ha…óata men ha…ďugol e fii laawol Alla Ngol, gom…óii men njaltinaama e galleeji amen e …ďi…ó…ďe amen?\" Nde hare nden farlanoo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe hucciti, si wanaa see…óaa…ďe e ma…ď…ďe. Alla Ko Anndu…óo too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  2,247,"Annabaajo ma…ď…ďe on maakani …ďe:\"Alla Imminanii on Taaluuta laam…óo\". ∆Āe mbi'i:\"Hol no laamu laatoraŇčta mo e hoore amen,ko menen …ďuri mo haandude e laamu,o rokkaaka yaajeende jawdi?\" O maaki:\"Alla Su…ďike mo e dow mo'on,O ∆Āeydi mo yaajeende ka ganndal e ka …ďanndu\". Alla No Rokka Laamu Makko Ngun on Mo O Muuyi,Alla ko Yaaju…óo […ďural] Anndu…óo"
  2,248,"Annabaajo ma…ď…ďe on maakani …ďe: \"Nganndee Maande Alla nden, ko nde Arkawal ngal arata on; dee∆īere no e ndeer maggal, immorde ka Joomi mo'on, e ko heddinoo ko aalo Muusaa e aalo Haaruuna en acci, hara Malaa'ika en no ronndii ngal. Pellet no e koo ko jaŇčtaa …óoo, Maande wonannde on; si o laatike gom…óim…ďe"
  2,249,"Nde Taaluuta yaltidunoo e konu ngun, o maaki: \"Alla No Jarribora on caangol: kala yar…óo e maggol o jeyaaka e am, kala mo me…óaali ngol ko on …óon jeyaa e am, si wanaa on √Īe…óir…óo junngo mun √Īe…óannde\". ∆Āe yari e caangol ngol si wanaa see…óaa…ďe e ma…ď…ďe. Nde o lummbunoo ngol, kaŇčko e …ďen gom…óim…ďe wondu…ďe e makko, …ďen mbi'i: \"Feere alanaa en e Jaaluuta e konu mun ngun\". ∆Āen fellitu…ďe hawray e Alla …ďen mbi'i: \"Heewii ka fedde tokosere fooliri fedde …óuu…óunde, duŇčayee Alla\". Pellet Alla No Wondi e mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen"
  2,250,"Nde …ďe fee√Īannoo Jaaluuta e konu mun ngun, …ďe mbi'i: \"Joomi amen, Rufu mu√Īal e dow amen, TabiŇčtinaa teppe amen, Faabo-…óaa men e …ďee heefer…ďe"
  2,251,"∆Āe fooliri…ďe DuŇčayee Alla: Daawuuda wari Jaaluuta, Alla Rokki mo Laamu e Annabaaku, O Anndini mo kon ko O Muuyi. Si wanaano Ko Alla Du√Īirnoo yim…ďe …ďen yoga e dow yoga, leydi ndin bonayno. Kono Alla Ko Jom ∆Āural e dow winndere nden"
  2,252,"∆äen ko Aayeeje Alla, Me…óen JaŇčnga …óe e dow maa…óa wondude e Goonga, Pellet ko a jeyaa…óo e Nulaa…ďe …ďen"
  2,253,"∆Āen Nulaa…ďe, Men ∆Āurnii yoga ma…ď…ďe e dow yoga : No e ma…ď…ďe yeewtidu…ďe e Alla, O ∆ĀaŇčti darjaaji yoga e ma…ď…ďe; Men Rokki Iisaa, …ďi…ó…óo Maryama on, …ďanngannduyeeji Men semmbiniri mo fittaandu laa…ďundu ndun. Si Alla Muuyuno, wom…ďe …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe …ďen wartindirtaano …ďaawo nde …ďanngannduyeeji …óin ari maab…ďe. Kono …ďe luutondiri: no e ma…ď…ďe …ďen gom…óim…ďe, no e ma…ď…ďe …ďen yeddu…ďe. Si Alla Muuyuno, …ďe wartindirtaano, kono Alla no wa…óa kon ko O Yi…ói"
  2,254,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, sakkee e kon ko Men Arsiki on adii √Īalaande arde; nde ngeyngu alaa e mayre, wanaa sehilaaku, wanaa tefoore. Ko heefer…ďe …ďen woni too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  2,255,"Alla, alaa reweteezo si wanaa kanko, Wuur…óo √Ďii…ďu…óo. ŇäoŇčre nanngataa Mo, wanaa kadi …óoyngol. ko Kanko Jeyi huunde ko woni ka kammuuli e huunde ko woni ka leydi. Ko hommbo woni on tefoowo ka Makko si wanaa e duŇčayee Makko? Himo anndi ko woni yeeso ma…ď…ďe, e ko woni …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āe hu…ďindotaako huunde e Anndal Makko ngal si wanaa ko O Muuyi. Jullere Makko nden no yaaji …ďuri kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Reenugol …ói aaninaa Mo. Ko Kano woni Toowu…óo Maw…óo On. @Corrected"
  2,256,"Doolugol alaa ka diina. Gom…óii peewal ngal …ďanngii immorde e majjere nden. Kala yeddu…óo …óuu…óa bewreeru ndun o gom…óini Alla, haray o jogitike …ďoggi finnde hoolaare …óin, firtagol alanaa …ói. Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,257,"Alla Ko Gi…óo gom…óim…ďe …ďen: Himo yaltina …ďe e ni…ďe, O na…ďa …ďe e ndaygu. ∆Āeya yeddu…ďe, yi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe ko …óuu…óa bewreeji …óin: Hi…ói yaltina …ďe e ndaygu na…ďa …ďe e ni…ďe. ∆Āen ko yim…ďe yiite, luttoo…ďe e magge"
  2,258,"E a yi'aali on wennju…óo Ibraahiima e fii Jey…óo mo On, fii Alla no Ye…ói mo laamu, nde Ibraahiima maakunoo: \"Jey…óo lam on, ko On Wuurnata Wara\". [Wennju…óo on] wi'i: \"Min kadi mi…óo wuurna wara\". Ibraahiima maaki: \"Pellet Alla no Addira naange ngen fu…ónaange, addir nge hiirnaange\".Yeddu…óo on mugaa. Alla fewnataa yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  2,259,"Wolla ko hono oon birtii…óo wuro yeewngo ngo maadi mum e mbildi mum yirbi o wi*i hono Alla wuurtaninta …óum caggal maayde mum? Alla wari mbo o lelii duu…ďi teemedere O ummini mbo O daali hono foti √Īii…ď…óa o wi*i √Īalawma maa feccere √Īalawma, O daali alah a duumiima …óo duu…ďi teemedere ∆īeew √Īaamdu ma e njaram ma waylaaki ndaaru mbabba ma ba, ngam min mba…ó ma maande wonande yim…ďe, ∆īeew ∆īi*e nomin cardata…óe refti Min muurda…óe teew, nde …óuum fee√Īi mbo o wi*i mi anndi Alla na hattani kala huunde…ď…ó∆ī∆ī√Īj"
  2,260,"Nde Ibraahiima maaki joom am hollam na nguurtanirta maay…ďe, O daali mate a goon…óinaani? o maaki ohonkay kono ko haa …ďernde am dee∆īa , O daali nanngu colli nay tappu…ói faade e ma refti mba…óa e kala tulde feccere e colli he refti noddu…ói …ói ngara e ma ho…ói njaha anndu Alla ko pooloowo mbo fooletaake ko O √Īee√Īo"
  2,261,Yeru …ďeen nafkoo…ďe e laawol Alla ko honbbere fu…ónunde butaali njee…ói…ói in wutaandu fof teemedere abbere Alla na sowana Mo O welaa Alla ko jaac…óo Ganndo
  2,262,Nafkoo…ďe jawdi mum en e laawol Alla refti …ďe ndewnatah e ko…ďe ko wacde wolla lor woodanii…ďe njobdi mum en ka joomi mum en kulol alanaa…ďe …ďe ngonah sunotoo…ďe
  2,263,"Konngol lobbol …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e sadaka dewnatee…óo lorla, Alla ko Gala yondanii…óo munyoowo"
  2,264,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ďe wotee mbonniree sadakuuji mon wacde e lorlude hono oon tottir…óo jawdi mum yeenga yim…ďe o goon…óinaani Alla e √Īalngu cakkatiingu o wayi kono haa∆īre …óaatnde to…ďo yani e mayre acci nde honde wa*i e teeleende …ďeen kattantah hay huunde e ko …ďe paggatii ko,Alla feewnatah yim…ďe heeferee…ďe …ďe"
  2,265,"Yeru …ďeen nafkoo…ďe jawdi mum en ngam …óa…ď…ďude welu Alla e tabatinde pittaali mum en ko hono ngesa ngonba e dow tulde to…ďo heewngo heewngo yani e heba ba, ba addi cowe …ói…ď…óe ko ba addatno si ba to…ďaam √Īuur √Īuur koba hecca mbelba balangol A na yi*a ko mba…óaton ko"
  2,266,"Mbela gooto e mon na yi…ói nde o da√Īata ngesa tamaro e inabeeje na ila e les mabba caatli te homba jogii e heba kala …ďeynaa…óe, o naywi hombo jogii …ďeyngu loongu henndu wondundu e yiite yana e ngesa he ba suma, ko hona nih Min …ďannganirta kaawisaaji …ói mbela miicta…óon"
  2,267,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ďe tottiree ko laa…ďi ummaade ko paggiti …óon e ko Min njaltinani on ka leydi, wotee paande ko so…ďi ko ngam nafkude heen on ngonah nanngoo…ďe …óum si wonah on meerni heen, ngannde Alla ko yondanii…óo Mantaa…óo"
  2,268,"Seytaane na fodana on baasal o yamira on pankare, Alla noon na fodana on yaafuya ummaade e Makko e …ďural Alla ko jaac…óo ko O Ganndo"
  2,269,"Hombo totta √Īee√Īal mbo O wela kala tottaa…óo √Īee√Īal o tottaa ma mo∆ī∆īere mawnde, siftortah …óum si wonah joman hakkiillaaji"
  2,270,"Kala ko tottir…óon e nafake wolla takku…óon e takkere pellet Alla na anndi …óuum, woodanaani too√Īoo…ďe walloo…ďe"
  2,271,Si on …ďannginii sadakeeji na ∆ī∆īi si on cuu…ói …ói tottu…óon …ói waas…ďe ko …óuum …ďuri on mo∆ī∆īande O hafrana on bon…ói mon Alla na humpitii ko golloton ko
  2,272,"A fawaaki peewal mum en kono ko Alla feewnata mbo O faala, kala ko tottir…óon e mo∆ī∆īere ko ko*e mon woodani on nafkatah si wonah ngam Alla kala ko tottir…óon e mo∆ī∆īere tottite …óum e mbaadi timmundi onon de on too√Īetaake"
  2,273,"Woodanii waas…ďe suraa…ďe gaa e laawol Alla …ďe mbaawah yaade e leydi hee, majju…ďe na cikka ko…ďe al…óu…ďe sabu …óuurnaade aduna ana anndira…ďe maandeeji mum en …ďe √Īaagataaka yim…ďe e mbaadi cattundi kala ko tottir…óon Alla na anndi …óum"
  2,274,"Tootiroo…ďe jawdi mum en jemma e √Īalawma e mbaadi mbirniindi e mbaadi …ďanngundi, …ďeen de woodanii…ďe njbdi mum en ummaade ka joomi mum en kulol woodanaani …ďe …ďe ngonah sunatoo…ďe"
  2,275,"…ďeen √Īaamoo…ďe riba …ďe ummataako si wonah no mbo seytaani memi …óuum noon ko sabu wiide …ďe pellet njeegu wa*i kono riba, Alla noon daknii njeeygu O harmini riba, kala mbo waaju ummmarii mbo ka Alla o acci woodanii mbo o …ďenni ko fiyaaku makko e Alla fawii, kala duttii…óo noon ko …ďeen ngoni joman en yiite saasoo…ďe e henge haa pooma"
  2,276,Alla na momto riba na …ďamta sadakuuji Alla yi…óah kala kee…óo keefeeru e bakkadinoowo sanne
  2,277,…ďeen goon…óin…ďe ngolli ko mo∆ī∆īi o darni juulde o tottiri askal woodanii…ďe jobdi mum en ummaade ko joomi mum en kulol alanaa…ďe …ďe ngonah sunatoo…ďe
  2,278,Eehey mon goon…óin…ďe kulee Alla accon ko heddii ko e riba si on ngonii goon…óu…ďe
  2,279,Si on mba…óaani …óuum kolliree hare ummorde e Alla e nelaa…óo MakkoJJJ…ďJ
  2,280,"Si tawii o wonii e satteende yo o mu√Īane haa e yaajeende,nde cakkorton …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e mon si on ngonii anndu…ďe"
  2,281,Kulee √Īalngu ngu nduttete…óon ka Alla refti yo…ďee kala fittaandu ko ndu faggitii ko kam…ďe …ďe too√Īetaake
  2,282,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ďe si on √Īamlandiri nyamaande faade happu dottaa…óo mbinndee nde, yo nuun…óu…óo winndu hakkunde mon, woto binndoowo sala winndude yo o winndu no Alla anndiniri mbo, yo o winndu yo mbo hakke woni dow mum winndu yo o hul joomiiko woto o ustu heen hay huunde, si wonii mbo hakke woni e dow mum ko …óaay…óo wolla loh…óo wollo o waawah fidde, yo keedo makko fidir nuun…óal, ceednee seede en …ói…óo e wor…ďe mon, si wor…ďe …ói…óo ngalah ko gorko e rew…ďe …ói…óo …ďe mbelete …óon e seedeeli ngam si gooto e ma…ď…ďe yrdditi go…ó…óo o siftirina mbo, woto seedeeli cala si…ďe noddaama, wote kaaste winndude ko fam…ói maa ko heewi faade e happu mum, ko …óuum …ďuri nuun…óude ka Alla …ďuri fooccaade wonande seede …ďuri kadi …ďadaade waasde mon sikkitaade, si wonah kommersaagu ngonaangu ngu yiilaton hakkunde mon, ndeen noon bakkaat alah e mon nde mbaasaton …óum winndude, ceetnee si on yeeyandiri woto binndoowo e seede lore, si on wa…óii …óuum pellet …óuum ko faasikaagal e mon, kulee Alla O anndina on Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde"
  2,283,"Si on ngonii e …óatngal on ke…ďaani binndoowo tottirre jukunnde tamaande, si on koolandirii, oon tottaa…óo hoolaare yo tottit hoolaare nde, yo o hul Alla joom makko, wotee cuu…óe seedanfaagu kala cuu…óo ngu pellet oon …ďernde makko ko bakkadinnde, Alla na anndi ko ngollaton ko"
  2,284,"Woodanii Alla ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi si on …ďannginii ko e pittaali mon wolla on cuu…ói ma Alla haasbu mon sabu mum, O yaafoo mbo O wela O lepta mbo wela, Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde"
  2,285,"Nulaa…óo goon…óanii ko jippinaa ko e Makko ummade e Joom Makko, e goonin…ďe …ďe fof …ďe goon…óanii Alla e malaykaaji Makko e defte makko e Nulaa…ďe makko, min ceerndatah hay gooto e Nulaa…ďe makko, …ďe wii min nanii min …óoftiima hafran amen Joomi amen ko Mah woni ruttorde"
  2,286,"Alla fawatah fittaandu kondu hattanaani,woodanii ndu kondu faggii, fawiima e dow mayru kondu faggitii,Joomi amen woto nanngir min ko min njjiti ko wollo ko min ngoopi ko,woto A faw e amen tampere hono no ndoondirna…óa …ďeen adii…ďe amen,Joomi amen woto faw min komin kattanaani,yaafa amin cuura bakkatuuJi amen nJurma…óa min ko Aan woni keeda amin wollu min e dow yim…ďe heeferee…ďe …ďe"